Requirements:
	- python (presumably > 2.5)
	- py-tweepy (http://code.google.com/p/tweepy/)

Installation:
	- install -c -m 755 src/follow-delta.py /somewhere/in/your/path/follow-delta
	- install -c -m 444 doc/follow-delta.1 /somewhere/in/your/manpath/man1/follow-delta.1

Questions/comments:
